A state to realize inner MPS(Mental positioning system)
============================================
Now a days who keep smart phone they use Google Maps to reach their destination. This is due to use of Global Positioning System(GPS) that tell your current location, destination location as well it also guide the shortest paths. At each and every step of movement GPS not only guiding the highlighting the current position but also it indicating the direction using touch type waves.
How it is easy to reach our destination by using this software. Before invention of this software we had also reach to destination but many times we had to ask here and there
even some time we reach to another destination and again from there we had search our correct destination.
ie it is not simple as GPS guide

